title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 15 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Dec 15 2021
description:
Psaki blames inflation on corporate greed of Big Meat -- and Clay and Buck reiterate a Rush point about socialism. TIME's Man of the Year, Elon Musk, slaps down "Senator Karen", Elizabeth Warren. It's amazing how fast the Defund the Police movement has turned tail. Senator Marsha Blackburn on Biden's "Build Back Broke" bill.
